***************************************************************
*                                                             *
*                  Very simple chat                           *
*                Created ~19 Aug 2017                         *
*                                                             *
***************************************************************
*                                                             *
*    PHP Version 7.1.6 - Tested                               *
*    Server Apache 2.4.25 - Tested                            *
*    SQLite Library 3.7.17 - Tested                           *
*                                                             *
*    Main start page                                          *
*    /mainpage/index.html                                     *
*                                                             *
***************************************************************
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /mainpage/index.html                                     |
|    Main page of webroom                                     |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /mainpage/styles.css                                     |
|    Styles for main page                                     |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /rooms/                                                  |
|    Directory where new rooms will be created                |
|    and be stored for a while                                |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /scripts/baseFunc.php                                    |
|    Set of base functions                                    |
|    Include values check, query results check and etc.       |
|    Included by other script (require_once)                  |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /scripts/config.php                                      |
|    Set of config to make connection with database           |
|    and generation COOKIESET                                 |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /scripts/createRoom.php                                  |
|    Script for room creating                                 |
|    Require config.php and baseFunc.php                      |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /scripts/deleteRoom.php                                  |
|    Script for room deleting                                 |
|    Require config.php and baseFunc.php                      |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /scripts/logInRoom.php                                   |
|    Script for log in room                                   |
|    Require config.php and baseFunc.php                      |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /simpleInit/docs/                                        |
|    Stores index.php....                                     |
|    Is mainly intended for                                   |
|    copy / create in the room                                |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /simpleInit/index.php                                    |
|    The file to be copied to the root of each room           |
|    Important for its work                                   |
|    Outside the room non-working                             |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /simpleInit/test.php                                     |      
|    The file to be copied to the root of each room           |
|    Important for its work                                   |
|    Outside the room non-working                             |
---------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------------------------
|    /SQL_CHATTABLE_CREATE_D_MADM/CHATTABLE.sql               |
|    SQL script for creating table                            |
---------------------------------------------------------------
